<span id="Sector_9:_BoundBox"></span>
===영역 9: 경계상자===

[[File:Macro_FCInfo_BoundBox_00.png|FCInfo BoundBox]]

*BoundBox gives extreme dimensions of the shape.
**maximum X length : {{LineEdit|10.0 mm}}
